Package: termcopy
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}
Description: CLI tool for terminal clipboard operations (OSC52)
 termcopy reads from stdin or a file, base64-encodes input,
 and prints an OSC 52 escape sequence suitable for copying
 text through terminal sessions.
